Here is a small Tutorial for installing, especially those who get the string errror

1.Open the rar file with winrar (or any other rar program)
2.Go to the FXhome_Visionlab rar file inside
3.Extract the VisionLabStudioWindows.programKey to your desktop (Or anywhere, as long as you can remember where you put it).
4.Open the Fxhome Visionlab installer inside the same rar file
5.Follow the installation
6. (You MUST turn off your internet before turning on Visionlab) Start up Visionlab, It will ask you for your program key, Just point it to where you saved it (It found mine automatically)
7. In Visionlab you need to go to Edit>>Preferences and uncheck the box "Check for Updates"
8. There, Your all done! and you won't get any errors and you can do it with your internet on.

Forgot to mention, there arent any presets in this to begin with i believe, just open the rar file called presets, go to Effects_Presets, Effect, And copy all those files in both of those rars into: C:\Program Files\FXHome Visionlab Studio\Presets

And there you go, You will have presets!
